    <section identifier="/ca-mountain-view/part-i/article-v/section-513"
             temporalId="sSection 513">
      <num>Section 513</num>
      <heading>Council action</heading>
      <content>
        <p>Legislative action shall be taken by the council only by means of an ordinance, resolution
               or minute action duly recorded in the official minutes of the city council. (As amended
               November 3, 1998.)</p>
      </content>
    </section>
  </main>
